<TEXT>
a preliminary investigation of rep newt 
gingrich is nearing its end with an apparent conclusion by an 
outside attorney that there are no grounds for a fullfledged 
ethics probe of the no 2 house republican leader capitol hill 
sources say 
but the final answer on whether the georgia republican is off 
