focused on the reaction of foreign markets which had been closed 
during the friday the 13th plummet he said 
it became clear as i stared at those statistics that it looked 
much more like a technical market change the us stock 
decline was picked up around the rest of the world but not added 
to that is an important distinction he said in an interview 
from the white house brady went to the treasury building and 
personally monitored developments on computer screens providing 
uptodate information simultaneously on stocks stock futures 
international currency and bond trading he said 
